  "texts": [
    "In the context of network security, quantum encryption may lead to new level of reliability and safety of the sensitive data, that was previously thought, to be unattainable.",
    "The dependency of nodes and events in today's networks is broader and is developing in terms of space and time.",
    "In such complex network configurations, the application of a contemporary technique for intrusion detection is offered by the ST-GCN or Spatial-Temporal Graph Convolutional Networks.",
    "Due to the fact that these networks depict such complex relationships in a very accurate manner, these kinds of networks excel in architectures where aspects such as layout and time play a role in the traffic of the network.",
    "ST-GCNs are constructed on top of graph convolutional networks, making them capable of handling the complexity of actual networks."
  ],
